message.body: Hi Eileen remembered that yesterday was Tony's birthday is the 25th Kathy's?Love Liz
Hi Liz - yes Kathy's is the 25th. Hope all is well with you. Love, Eileen
How's that ankle of yours?better I hope & thanks 4 getting back to me
The ankle is not great but getting there. It was fractured and it's rough getting around in this snow. Just started PT last Thursday.
That PT is important tom is going once a week now that he's back to work but does it at home every day.he was going 3xs/week for last 2 months.
